<!-- About Content -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container about-page-grid">
    <div class="about-main">
      <span class="section-tag">Our Story</span>
      <h2>History & Background</h2>
      <p>Pimpri Chinchwad College of Engineering (PCCOE) was established in <strong>1999</strong> by the Pimpri Chinchwad Education Trust (PCET) in Sector 26, Pradhikaran, Nigdi, Pune – 411044. The institution has grown from a single campus to a sprawling 40-acre green campus hosting over 6,000 students.</p>
      <p>Affiliated to <strong>Savitribai Phule Pune University (SPPU)</strong>, PCCOE received autonomous status in 2009, enabling it to design its own curriculum aligned with industry needs. The institution has consistently produced top engineers working at leading organizations worldwide.</p>
      <p>PCCOE is accredited with <strong>NAAC A+ grade</strong> and several programs carry <strong>NBA accreditation</strong>. The college is consistently ranked among the top 50 engineering colleges in India by NIRF.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-sidebar">
      <div class="info-card">
        <h4>🏛️ Quick Facts</h4>
        <table class="info-table">
          <tr><td>Established</td><td><strong>1999</strong></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Trust</td><td><strong>PCET</strong></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Affiliation</td><td><strong>SPPU, Pune</strong></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Status</td><td><strong>Autonomous</strong></td></tr>
          <tr><td>NAAC Grade</td><td><strong>A+</strong></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Campus Area</td><td><strong>40 Acres</strong></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Students</td><td><strong>6000+</strong></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Faculty</td><td><strong>300+</strong></td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Vision & Mission -->
<section class="section vm-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag">Our Purpose</span>
      <h2>Vision, Mission & Values</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="vm-grid">
      <div class="vm-card vm-vision">
        <div class="vm-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>Vision</h3>
        <p>To be a globally recognized institution for producing technically competent, innovative, and socially responsible engineers who contribute significantly to industry, society, and the nation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vm-card vm-mission">
        <div class="vm-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3>Mission</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Impart quality technical education with state-of-the-art infrastructure.</li>
          <li>Foster research, innovation, and entrepreneurship culture.</li>
          <li>Develop industry-academia collaborations for experiential learning.</li>
          <li>Mold students into ethical and environmentally conscious professionals.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="vm-card vm-values">
        <div class="vm-icon">🌟</div>
        <h3>Core Values</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>🔷 <strong>Integrity</strong> – Honesty in all endeavors</li>
          <li>🔷 <strong>Innovation</strong> – Fostering creative thinking</li>
          <li>🔷 <strong>Inclusion</strong> – Equal opportunity for all</li>
          <li>🔷 <strong>Excellence</strong> – Striving for the highest standards</li>
          <li>🔷 <strong>Service</strong> – Commitment to society</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

